{"tid":115745,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家)旅客看不到極光　竟圍毆芬蘭導遊 (18:38)","createTime":"2017-02-10T18:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T18:58:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23365df5f52af4208ed9cf67ae5bb18a88b66d51","tid":115745,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFtMz48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFtMz48.jpg&h=bdd9af62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時至4月是看極光的最佳季節，吸引大批旅客到訪芬蘭等地。挪威廣播公司（NRK）報道，一群中國遊客因為沒有看到北極光，圍毆他們的芬蘭導遊。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n挪威廣播公司（NRK）昨日(9日)報道，一群中國旅客跟隨名為「北極光之旅」旅遊，疑因不滿沒有看見極光，圍毆芬蘭導遊，導遊打電話報警，警方到場協調，並向中國遊客解釋，導遊無法決定極光是否會出現。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方向記者指，導遊感到十分恐懼，因為眾多憤怒的中國遊客將他們包圍起來，他們指從來沒有遇到過如此場面。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當天是陰天，因此很難看到北極光。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170210/s00004/1486721492826#sthash.zgFfWFOR.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170210%2Fs00004%2F1486721492826%23sthash.zgFfWFOR.dpuf&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=19a65c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170210%2Fs00004%2F1486721492826%23sthash.zgFfWFOR.dpuf&h=fa4c27e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170210/s00004/1486721492826#sthash.zgFfWFOR.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"8fa502bf119a975ec4583f357fcac3979a8f04f7","tid":115745,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b341fae1009787a27dbc8f2fcf386ae9eecda2b","tid":115745,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"中國最好笑的景點是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk